    schema1:description "Natalie Armstrong is Professor of Healthcare Improvement Research at the University of Leicester, where she is also Implementation Lead for the NIHR Applied Research Collaboration – East Midlands (ARC-EM). Natalie is experienced in applying social science theory and methods to the area of healthcare implementation and improvement research."@en ;
